<template>Show {{ post.value }}</template>
<script setup>
import { ref } from "vue";
import axios from "axios";
const post = ref([]);

axios
  .get("https://hacker-news.firebaseio.com/v0/item/126809.json?print=pretty")
  .then((response) => {
    post.value.push(response.data);
    console.log(post.value[0]);
  })
  .catch((error) => {
    console.error("Error fetching data:", error);
  });
</script>
